{"tid":1498952,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"7.21元朗恐襲 再有一男子被控參與暴動","createTime":"2019-08-23T14:35:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-23T15:00:15.000Z","uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d80f0ccf06117991b25a59e6da6d39b9895718ae","tid":1498952,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"7.21「元朗恐襲」白衣人無差別襲擊市民，導致45人受傷，事隔逾一個月，警方只拘捕28人，日前終落案起訴兩名男子暴動罪，案件今午提堂。據控方案情指，案發當日在西鐵站大堂分別有白衣及黑衣人口角，並指雙方均有使用暴力，包括投擲水樽及使用西鐵站內的消防喉射水等。兩被告被閉路電視拍得身處其中，又指首被告以垃圾桶蓋向人施襲。案件押後至10月25日再訊，其間兩人獲准保釋候訊。另外，新界北總區重案組人員經進一步調查後，今日於青衣再拘捕一名48歲本地男子涉嫌「參與暴動」，他現正被扣留調查。<br />\n<br />\n上月21日傍晚，大批白衣暴徒已在西鐵元朗站附近街道集結，持藤條襲擊途人，入夜後他們闖入元朗站無差別襲擊乘客，多人被打至滿身傷痕，亦有記者遇襲；白衫暴徒深夜再施襲，到場義載街坊的前傳媒人柳俊江更被打至頭破血流，事件令至少45名市民受傷送院。警隊連日來被炮轟縱容鄉黑集結，又延遲39分鐘才到場未能保護市民，當晚更零拘捕，任由暴徒離開。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190823/59967194\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190823%2F59967194&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=5a4abad4\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Fbreaking%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190823%2F59967194&h=f06acf10\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/breaking/realtime/article/20190823/59967194</a>"},{"pid":"ebf3190ee1b878e51c419f82642d9563381118ce","tid":1498952,"uid":125079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:36:43.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-visas-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpetitions.whitehouse.gov%2Fpetition%2Frevoke-visas-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests&d=3B0aCwotxrbiSqfA1QWlAkkSG0DzaVerHR9pE4rwCb4%3D&h=68d996c1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://petitions.whitehouse.gov/petition/revoke-visas-chinese-college-students-who-disrupted-otherwise-peaceful-pro-hong-kong-protests</a><br />\n<br />\n要求美國撤銷妨礙反送中示威的中國留學生之學生簽證，並進一步收緊中國留學簽證"},{"pid":"2aeda0b4830f4f6ba5d066bb9ef22e3cd6df6593","tid":1498952,"uid":169079,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T14:39:28.000Z","msg":"據控方案情指，案發當日在西鐵站大堂分別有白衣及黑衣人口角，並指雙方均有使用暴力<br />\n咩撚野事呀，比人打都叫雙方都有暴力？我屌你老母咩"},{"pid":"1f999a29560e23d4828432183de222ba13deec75","tid":1498952,"uid":281926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-23T15:00:15.000Z","msg":"各位巴打絲打，頂住呀！<br />\n路還很長，記住齊上齊落！<br />\n香港人可攻可守，智勇雙全！<br />\n記住<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong>永不分化！不割蓆！不篤灰！</strong></span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: violet;\"><strong>It&rsquo;s now or never</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">824 機場復活，WE WANT YOU！而家搭車犯法呀？</span></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/K9EGvnL.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FK9EGvnL.jpg&h=9da42bc4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/WKSEg2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FWKSEg2M.jpg&h=20a2e6bd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/now5W2M.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fnow5W2M.jpg&h=db034c66&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/rC19Ef7.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FrC19Ef7.jpg&h=5ab15f09&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/KUdLW2O.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FKUdLW2O.jpg&h=132e85dd&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qBGBjf8.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqBGBjf8.jpg&h=8a441805&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\